                "listType": "bullet"
              },
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": "Why is this different?",
                    "textStyle": {
                      "fontWeight": "bold"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              },
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": "Even though these machines don’t run in Azure’s datacenters, once connected, they appear inside Azure."
                  }
                ],
                "listType": "bullet"
              },
              {
                "textRuns": [
                  {
                    "value": "In Azure, the can gain tags, use Azure Policy, and can be monitored or secured just like ordinary Azure VMs."
